        "name": "Vortex Viper HS 2.5x10 30mm riflescope",
        "shortName": "Viper HS",
        "description": "An extremely versatile hunting scope that is also useful for fun or sports shooting to some extent. The wide angled, large lens offers a large view field at the minimum, 2.5x magnification, which is perfect for stalking prey, while the 10x maximum magnification still gives the possibility to hit anything that might have gotten away. The very fine, SFP reticle is true at maximal magnification to help with shot placement at longer ranges, especially with the great and easy to use Dead-Hold BDC reticle."
